@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "User Interface\n(UI)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System)" as Backend

Officer -> UI : 1: approve or reject vessel visit notification
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (ApproveVvnDto / RejectVvnDto)
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (VesselVisitNotificationDto)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Officer : 1.3: display decision confirmation
deactivate UI

@enduml
